OL,5, The UK government's push to revive     
OL,6, imperial measurements is "utter        
OL,7, nonsense" and will cost businesses, a  
OL,8, leading retail boss has said.          
OL,10,FThe government has launched a review of
OL,11,Fhow traders can use the UK's           
OL,12,Ftraditional weighing system for goods. 
OL,14,FBritish shops had to use metric        
OL,15,Fmeasurements under EU rules, with the  
OL,16,Foption to show imperial equivalents -  
OL,17,Fpounds and ounces - alongside.         
OL,19,FBut critics say the review is nostalgic
OL,20,Fand could burden businesses.           
